Package: classo
Type: Package
Title: Customized Penalized Regression Incorporating External Information
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Chubing Zeng
Maintainer: Chubing Zeng <chubingz@usc.edu>
Description: R package for Empirical Bayes tuning and Customized Lasso with External Information. 
     Empirical Bayes tuning provides an way to estimating tuning parameter in Lasso as 
     an alternative to cross validation. Customized Lasso generalizes standard Lasso by 
     allowing differential shrinkage for parameters, with the goal of improving prediction. 
